      "content": "i see. so it wasn't just random hate, it was actually structured around these specific metrics. for my paper, i need to describe the actual logic they applied. like, if they were looking at a specific group, how would they have characterized their \"natural\" tendencies or social behaviors based on those measurements? i'm trying to write a section on how they mapped these physical traits onto social outcomes like criminality or social stability.",
